{"tid":1826964,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台北十分-放天燈店推薦","createTime":"2020-01-16T14:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T14:48:53.000Z","uid":302558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c21e19feb47635bb70d2ab6f21d1ead6debd562e","tid":1826964,"uid":302558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"大家好！<br />\n我之前去左台北十份放天燈<br />\n遇到一間好好既店主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藝巧傳統天燈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZPTHB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZPTHB4.jpg&h=78f7b6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主好好人，5色天燈都係賣150，其他店賣200！<br />\n同埋會幫你影哂咁多面天燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置係十分車站對面街道<br />\n行到最尾就係啦！<br />\n請大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74569ee51e3b8b906de1e792b8119504db3e41c1","tid":1826964,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"有無五大訴求"},{"pid":"59b55d1eeacff5a9118bcb7b3db913799fc866d6","tid":1826964,"uid":54460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"仲放天燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf9fe34a6a8a53a39ed3bccbfbad80c00b503c0","tid":1826964,"uid":302558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59b55d1eeacff5a9118bcb7b3db913799fc866d6","tid":1826964,"uid":54460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"仲放天燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"當然明白係會破壞環境<br />\n但係如果有人選擇去放<br />\n都希望支持一下好人店主"}]}